      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "Funny enough to see Oracle/Sun describe it that way as null is an instance of all types. Anyhow, as you said, the pure meaning of it is &quot;I could write any type here as I am not interested in it, so I will put Void to make sure people who read my code understand exactly that&quot;"
